      "content": "it just feels so heavy. like i'm just a shell of a person moving through a world that doesn't actually need anything from me. people talk about \"resilience\" or \"finding a new passion\" but that feels like such a lie when you're just... empty. why bother even trying to exist if there's nothing left inside to give?",
